  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A visual novel with a fabulous atmosphere where your every choice matters.</h2><br>Ruff and his brothers went to haymaking one day. His brothers punished him — do not lie down in the heat on the boundary under a broom bush. Did not listen to the brothers Ruff. This is where his misadventures began.<br><br>\"Navi tales: the Book of Gypsies\" is a visual novel, from the pages of which the midday summer heat is bursting. The setting is based on Slavic folklore. <br><br>\"Navi Tales\" is a prequel to another game of our studio - \"Navi Day\".",
